data.description: Cambridge -stunning Cape Cod in water oriented neighborhood! Beautiful kitchen with granite counters , stainless appliances plus a wine fridge.  Lots of charming accents - the dining room flows to a large sunken living room with upgraded molding.  Family room with pellet stove and sliders to the cool outdoor spaces -sitting area, fire pit - mature plantings are a gardeners delight. Primary bedroom features a bath with double vanity, 2 additional generous bedrooms. plus a second upgraded full bath. There is an extra room currently used as a playroom and laundry room that could  be another bedroom.  New shop 24 x 12 with heat and electric - great for crafters or DIY. There is an additional shed for lawn mower etc.   Large attic space great for storage or maybe expanded living space. The feel of country but minutes from Cambridge! Large floored attic may offer expansion possibilities.
